                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12667879" author="ryanobjc" created="Wed, 28 Jan 2009 00:06:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;d probably want to avoid spanning a cluster across datacenter boundaries... it&apos;s too easy to get into irreconcilable network splits.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Replication as a site-to-site backup is a great approach.  Multi-master replication would allow concurrent read/write when the link between the sites is down, but the internet connection is still available (very common scenario surprisingly).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think we need a statistical &apos;eventual consistency&apos; multi-write (Eg: paxos), but instead a straight forward replication stream (a la redo log replication from Oracle, mysql, etc) would be pretty good.  Tools to monitor that replication stream (replicas are X seconds behind kind of thing) would also be necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12667880" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 28 Jan 2009 00:11:48 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think we need a statistical &apos;eventual consistency&apos; multi-write (Eg: paxos), but instead a straight forward replication stream (a la redo log replication from Oracle, mysql, etc) would be pretty good. Tools to monitor that replication stream (replicas are X seconds behind kind of thing) would also be necessary.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for your input. I was also thinking that something like MySQL replication would be good enough for a majority of people at this point.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12668229" author="apurtell" created="Wed, 28 Jan 2009 23:25:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 for log shipping.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12707862" author="apurtell" created="Mon, 11 May 2009 01:25:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, I opened &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1295&quot; title=&quot;Multi data center replication&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1295&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1295&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; because I had forgotten about this issue. Close this issue in favor of 1295? Or vice versa?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12711031" author="stack" created="Wed, 20 May 2009 06:25:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lets favor hbase-1295 over this one.  Closing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
